  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/1b50265c8f80c5fcaa28293edd8f914c.poster.avif?t=1639926769\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/1b50265c8f80c5fcaa28293edd8f914c.webm?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/1b50265c8f80c5fcaa28293edd8f914c.mp4?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Depart on a trip with Anna, who lost her sight, to help cute animal friends and escape the dark reality. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/f16782b32c40f7cd3be4bcdd3fd0f3e5.poster.avif?t=1639926769\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/f16782b32c40f7cd3be4bcdd3fd0f3e5.webm?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/f16782b32c40f7cd3be4bcdd3fd0f3e5.mp4?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nid, who leads Anna in an unstable world, is a mysterious tree that shrunk for reasons unknown. Help Nid grow into its original state. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/b9bf5627b7e460a041bc4a4c669fcebf.poster.avif?t=1639926769\" width=440 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/b9bf5627b7e460a041bc4a4c669fcebf.webm?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446750/extras/b9bf5627b7e460a041bc4a4c669fcebf.mp4?t=1639926769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You'll face various problems in the town as a character that transforms into animals. Relax by helping Anna heal her emotional wounds that spread like darkness through reality.",
